[
  {
    "startTime": 20.336,
    "endTime": 24.799999999999997,
    "text": "All right, listen, I didn't wanna have to do this, but you leave me no choice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.4,
    "endTime": 26.799999999999997,
    "text": "Here comes the smolder."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.7,
    "endTime": 37.900000000000006,
    "text": "This is kind of an off day for me; this doesn't normally happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Fine, I'll take you to see the lanterns."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.1,
    "endTime": 42.1,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.3,
    "endTime": 44.199999999999996,
    "text": "Oops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.3,
    "endTime": 45.699999999999996,
    "text": "You broke my smolder."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.4,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Best day ever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.8,
    "endTime": 65.89999999999999,
    "text": "You know, I can't help but notice you seem a little at war with yourself here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.4,
    "endTime": 67.5,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.6,
    "endTime": 71.69999999999999,
    "text": "Now, I'm only picking up bits and pieces, of course, over-protective mother, forbidden road trip..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.8,
    "endTime": 73.3,
    "text": "I mean, this is serious stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.8,
    "endTime": 77.1,
    "text": "But let me ease your conscience: This is part of growing up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.2,
    "endTime": 81.4,
    "text": "A little rebellion, a little adventure⏤that's good, healthy even."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.2,
    "endTime": 84.2,
    "text": "You think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.3,
    "endTime": 85.39999999999999,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.5,
    "endTime": 87.4,
    "text": "You're way overthinking this, trust me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.5,
    "endTime": 88.7,
    "text": "Does your mother deserve it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.8,
    "endTime": 89.8,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.9,
    "endTime": 91.60000000000001,
    "text": "Would this break her heart and crush her soul?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.7,
    "endTime": 92.7,
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.8,
    "endTime": 94.89999999999999,
    "text": "But you've just got to do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 97.3,
    "text": "Break her heart?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.6,
    "endTime": 98.69999999999999,
    "text": "In half."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.8,
    "endTime": 100.39999999999999,
    "text": "Crush her soul?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.3,
    "endTime": 102.39999999999999,
    "text": "Like a grape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.5,
    "endTime": 105.4,
    "text": "She would be heartbroken; you're right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.5,
    "endTime": 107.7,
    "text": "I am, aren't I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.8,
    "endTime": 109.2,
    "text": "Oh, bother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.9,
    "endTime": 114.30000000000001,
    "text": "All right, I can't believe I'm saying this, but I'm letting you out of the deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.2,
    "endTime": 116.10000000000001,
    "text": "- What?  - That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.2,
    "endTime": 119.7,
    "text": "But don't thank me; let's just turn around and get you home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.8,
    "endTime": 120.8,
    "text": "Here's your pan, here's your frog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.9,
    "endTime": 128.5,
    "text": "I get back my satchel, you get back a mother-daughter relationship based on mutual trust, and voilà! We part ways as unlikely friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.7,
    "endTime": 129.7,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.8,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "I am seeing those lantern⏤"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.1,
    "endTime": 134.79999999999998,
    "text": "Oh, come on! What is it gonna take for me to get my satchel back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.8,
    "endTime": 136.70000000000002,
    "text": "I will use this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.2,
    "endTime": 143.5,
    "text": "Well, I've gotta say, didn't know you had that in you back there; that was pretty..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.4,
    "endTime": 145.20000000000002,
    "text": "- ... impressive.  - I know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.1,
    "endTime": 148.2,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.7,
    "endTime": 157.5,
    "text": "I know not who you are, nor how I came to find you, but may I just say..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.9,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 164.3,
    "text": "How you doin'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.4,
    "endTime": 165.5,
    "text": "The name's Flynn Rider."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.2,
    "endTime": 169.29999999999998,
    "text": "How's your day going, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.6,
    "endTime": 174.2,
    "text": "Who else knows my location, Flynn Rider?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.3,
    "endTime": 176.10000000000002,
    "text": "- All right, Blondie.  - Rapunzel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.5,
    "endTime": 177.5,
    "text": "Gesundheit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.6,
    "endTime": 178.7,
    "text": "Flynn!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 185.5,
    "text": "Flynn, look out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.7,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "You should see your faces because you look⏤"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.6,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Ridiculous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.8,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "We made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.5,
    "endTime": 228.7,
    "text": "Her hair glows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.8,
    "endTime": 229.5,
    "text": "We're alive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.6,
    "endTime": 231.2,
    "text": "I'm... I'm alive!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.3,
    "endTime": 232.3,
    "text": "I didn't see that coming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.4,
    "endTime": 234.3,
    "text": "- Eugene.  - The hair actually glows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.4,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "- Eugene.  - Why does her hair glow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.1,
    "endTime": 237.29999999999998,
    "text": "- Eugene!  - What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.2,
    "endTime": 241.29999999999998,
    "text": "It doesn't just glow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.9,
    "endTime": 245.4,
    "text": "Why is he smiling at me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.3,
    "endTime": 260.40000000000003,
    "text": "Please don't freak out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.6,
    "endTime": 266.70000000000005,
    "text": "Ah.... I'm not freaking out; are you freaking out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.8,
    "endTime": 270.1,
    "text": "No, I'm just very interested in your hair and the magical qualities that it possesses."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.2,
    "endTime": 272.09999999999997,
    "text": "How long has it been doing that exactly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.6,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Uh, forever, I guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.3,
    "endTime": 277.3,
    "text": "You okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.3,
    "endTime": 279.6,
    "text": "I'm terrified."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.9,
    "endTime": 281.9,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.1,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": "I've been looking out a window for 18 years, dreaming about what it might feel like when those lights rise in the sky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.5,
    "endTime": 297.3,
    "text": "What if it's not everything I dreamed it would be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.7,
    "endTime": 300.9,
    "text": "It will be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.8,
    "endTime": 304.2,
    "text": "And what if it is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.5,
    "endTime": 307.0,
    "text": "What do I do then?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.6,
    "endTime": 309.5,
    "text": "Well, that's the good part, I guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.3,
    "endTime": 312.3,
    "text": "You get to go find a new dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.5,
    "endTime": 316.2,
    "text": "I know what the big question is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.0,
    "endTime": 318.8,
    "text": "Did Rapunzel and I ever get married?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.9,
    "endTime": 325.5,
    "text": "Well, I'm pleased to tell you, that after years and years of asking and asking and asking..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.9,
    "endTime": 328.7,
    "text": "I finally said yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.8,
    "endTime": 330.5,
    "text": "Eugene."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.6,
    "endTime": 333.20000000000005,
    "text": "All right, I asked her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.3,
    "endTime": 335.90000000000003,
    "text": "And we're living happily ever after."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.6,
    "endTime": 337.70000000000005,
    "text": "Yes, we are."
  }
]